        "r1": {
            "name": "Martin K.",
            "text": "Amazing place with a one-of-a-kind atmosphere. The craft beers are excellent, the staff is friendly, and the courtyard garden — a perfect escape from the city center. We come here regularly for the quizzes.",
            "date": "2 weeks ago"
        },
        "r2": {
            "name": "Tereza M.",
            "text": "Finally a bar where you can actually sit down without noise and queues. Outstanding wine selection, the pet-nats are fantastic. We used the private room for a birthday and it was exactly what we wanted.",
            "date": "a month ago"
        },
        "r3": {
            "name": "Jakub P.",
            "text": "The best urban hideout in Prague. You come for one beer, you leave three hours later with a new favorite board game. The staff is lovely and knows what to recommend. I'll be back.",
            "date": "3 weeks ago"
        }
    }
},
